s%2Fisrael-offering-5-million-reward-for-each-gaza-hostage-freed-netanyahu-7058791%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20Israel%20was%20offering%20a%20reward%20of%20%245%20million%20to%20anybody%20who%20brings%20out%20a%20hostage%20held%20in%20Gaza.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-offering-5-million-reward-for-each-gaza-hostage-freed-netanyahu-7058791%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BExposed%26quot%3B%3A%20BJP%20Alleges%20Bitcoin%20Scam%20In%20Maharashtra%20Poll%2C%20Supriya%20Sule%20Reacts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20Congress%20and%20ally%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20faction%20of%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20have%20been%20hit%20by%20corruption%20allegations%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20crucial%20state%20elections.%20A%20retired%20police%20officer%2C%20Ravindranath%20Patil%2C%20%C2%A0has%20accused%20Mr%20Pawar's%20daughter%20Supriya%20Sule%20%C2%A0and%20state%20Congress%20chief%20Nana%20Patole%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20%C2%A0a%20fraud%20case%20involving%20cryptocurrency%20that%20dates%20back%20to%202018.%20The%20funds%2C%20he%20alleged%2C%20have%20been%20used%20for%20campaigning%20in%20the%20assembly%20election.%20Supriya%20Sule%20has%20denied%20any%20wrongdoing%20and%20called%20it%20the%20%26quot%3Bfamiliar%20tactics%20of%20spreading%20false%20information%20to%20manipulate%20the%20righteous%20voters%26quot%3B%20the%20night%20before%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20was%20quick%20to%20take%20note%20of%20the%20allegations%20and%20presented%20the%20media%20with%20audio%20clips%20it%20claimed%20were%20evidence%20of%20involvement%20of%20Nana%20Patole%20and%20Supriya%20Sule%20in%20what%20it%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3Bbitcoin%20scam%26quot%3B.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20spokesperson%20Sudhanshu%20Trivedi%20claimed%20the%20development%20has%20%26quot%3Bunmasked%26quot%3B%20the%20Opposition%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20and%20demanded%20replies%20from%20the%20Congress%20and%20Ms%20Sule%2C%20who%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20from%20Baramati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20amused%20that%20elections%20have%20come%20down%20to%20such%20a%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20Supriya%20Sule%20told%20NDTV.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSudhanshu%20Trivedi%20made%20five%20allegations%20and%20asked%20me%20five%20questions%20and%20they%20(the%20allegations)%20are%20all%20false.%20I%20am%20happy%20to%20sit%20with%20him%20in%20any%20public%20forum%20--%20place%20time%20and%20forum%20of%20his%20choice.%20It%20is%20all%20false%20and%20I%20have%20lodged%20a%20cybercrime%20complaint.%20I%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20any%20transfer%20of%20bitcoin...%20this%20shows%20the%20BJP's%20desperation%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20underscored%20her%20response%20with%20a%20series%20of%20posts%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EFamiliar%20tactics%20of%20spreading%20false%20information%20to%20manipulate%20the%20righteous%20voters%20are%20being%20resorted%20to%2C%20a%20night%20before%20the%20polling%20day.%20We%20have%20filed%20a%20criminal%20complaint%20to%20the%20Hon'ble%20ECI%20%26amp%3B%20the%20Cyber%20crime%20department%20against%20the%20fake%20allegations%20made%20of%20bitcoin...%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fg8Selv1DFk%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fg8Selv1DFk%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Supriya%20Sule%20(%40supriya_sule)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsupriya_sule%2Fstatus%2F1858910827090506106%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2019%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIt's%20appalling%20that%20such%20baseless%20allegations%20are%20made%20by%20Mr%20Sudhanshu%20Trivedi%2C%20yet%20not%20surprising%20as%20it's%20a%20clear%20case%20of%20spreading%20false%20information%2C%20the%20night%20before%20elections.%20My%20lawyer%20will%20be%20issuing%20a%20criminal%20%26amp%3B%20civil%20defamation%20notice%20against%20Sudhanshu%20Trivedi%20for%20making...%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Supriya%20Sule%20(%40supriya_sule)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsupriya_sule%2Fstatus%2F1858927836494717169%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2019%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patil%2C%20who%20had%20taken%20voluntary%20retirement%20from%20the%20Indian%20Police%20Service%2C%20was%20roped%20in%20by%20the%20Pune%20police%20along%20with%20cyber%20expert%20Pankaj%20Ghode%20to%20investigate%20a%20couple%20of%20cryptocurrency%20cases%20registered%20in%202018.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20had%20alleged%20that%20Mr%20Patil%2C%20in%20course%20of%20the%20investigation%2C%20transferred%20some%20cryptocurrencies%20into%20%C2%A0his%20account.%20Ghode%20had%20provided%20screenshots%20of%20the%20accounts%20to%20police%20by%20changing%20the%20numbers%20--%20that%20showed%20lesser%20amount%20in%20crypto%20wallets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patil%20had%20told%20reporters%20that%20he%20was%20framed%20which%20he%20and%20his%20colleagues%20have%20investigated%2C%20reported%20news%20agency%20IANS.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20a%20key%20witness%20in%20the%20case%2C%20Gaurav%20Mehta-an%20employee%20of%20an%20audit%20firm-had%20told%20him%20about%20the%202018%20cryptocurrency%20fraud%20investigation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMehta%20has%20alleged%20that%20during%20the%20arrest%20of%20Amit%20Bhardwaj%2C%20a%20cryptocurrency%20trader%2C%20a%20hardware%20wallet%20containing%20Bitcoin%20was%20seized.%20But%20the%20wallet%20was%20replaced%20by%20another%20one%20--%20allegedly%20under%20the%20direction%20of%20Amitabh%20Gupta%2C%20the%20then-Pune%20Police%20Commissioner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMehta%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20real%20culprits%20were%20Gupta%20and%20his%20team%20and%20Patil%20and%20his%20colleagues%20were%20arrested%20unjustly%2C%20It%20was%20also%20he%20who%20had%20given%20him%20the%20information%20about%20Nana%20Patole%20and%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatil%20told%20IANS%20that%20Mehta%20sent%20several%20voice%20recordings%20on%20'Signal'%20--%20social%20media%20app%20--%20including%20messages%20from%20Supriya%20Sule%20requesting%20cash%20in%20exchange%20for%20Bitcoin.%20In%20the%20recordings%2C%20Sule%20allegedly%20assured%20Mehta%20that%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%20worry%20about%20the%20investigation%2C%20as%20they%20would%20handle%20it%20once%20they%20came%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20recording%20reportedly%20featured%20Nana%20Patole%2C%20inquiring%20about%20the%20delay%20in%20the%20cash%20transaction.%20Though%20the%20audio%20messages%20are%20available%20with%20IANS%2C%20the%20agency%20does%20not%20vouch%20for%20the%20veracity%20of%20the%20clips.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732042320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fuqb20po_supriya-sule_625x300_11_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-polls-maharashtra-election-nana-patole-exposed-bjp-alleges-bitcoin-scam-in-maharashtra-poll-supriya-sule-reacts-7058310%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20former%20police%20officer%20has%20accused%20Congress%20State%20President%20Nana%20Patole%20and%20senior%20NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%20leader%20Supriya%20Sule%20of%20using%20Bitcoins%20to%20fund%20their%20campaign%20for%20the%20Maharashtra%20polls.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-polls-maharashtra-election-na