agement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fnetizens-react-to-ar-rahman-and-saira-banus-separation-who-are-we-to-judge-and-pass-comments%2Farticleshow%2F115461828.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amid%20Souring%20Ties%20With%20India%2C%20Canada's%20Latest%20Move%20Inconveniences%20Fliers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20growing%20tension%20between%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Ottawa%2C%20passengers%20travelling%20from%20Canada%20to%20India%20are%20being%20subjected%20to%20extra%20security%20screening%20now.%20This%20decision%20was%20announced%20by%20Canada's%20Transport%20Minister%20Anita%20Anand%20late%20on%20Monday%20evening%2C%20as%20part%20of%20new%20temporary%20protocols%2C%20implemented%20%26quot%3Bout%20of%20an%20abundance%20of%20caution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTransport%20Canada%20has%20implemented%20temporary%20additional%20security%20screening%20measures%2C%26quot%3B%20for%20travellers%20to%20India%2C%20Ms%20Anand%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20Canadian%20broadcaster%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20Follow%2C%20No%20Index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fcanada-increase-screening-india-1.7386941%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECBC%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPassengers%20%26quot%3Bmay%20experience%20some%20screening%20delays%20while%20these%20measures%20are%20in%20place.%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20enhanced%20security%20protocols%20will%20be%20implemented%20by%20the%20Canadian%20Air%20Transport%20Security%20Authority%20(CATSA)%2C%20the%20agency%20responsible%20for%20screening%20passengers%20and%20their%20baggage%20before%20entering%20the%20restricted%20areas%20of%20Canadian%20airports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20view%20of%20the%20new%20protocols%2C%20Air%20Canada%20has%20warned%20passengers%20bound%20for%20Indian%20destinations%20of%20l