%22%3ESuhana%20Khan%20playfully%20celebrated%20her%20brother%20Aryan%20Khan's%20directorial%20debut%20announcement%20for%20a%20Netflix%20India%20series.%20Sharing%20the%20news%20on%20Instagram%2C%20she%20expressed%20excitement%20and%20pride%2C%20hinting%20at%20the%20project's%20blend%20of%20humor%2C%20drama%2C%20and%20action.%20This%20announcement%20marks%20another%20milestone%20for%20the%20Khan%20family%20as%20Aryan%20follows%20in%20his%20father's%20footsteps.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsuhana-khan-teases-brother-aryan-khan-as-his-directorial-debut-gets-announced-just-like-it-always-is-with-you%2Farticleshow%2F115460843.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amid%20Russia-Ukraine%20Conflict%2C%20Why%20These%20Countries%20Are%20Preparing%20For%20War%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESeveral%20European%20countries%20are%20advising%20their%20residents%20to%20be%20ready%20for%20war%20even%20as%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%20witnessed%20a%20grim%20milestone%20recently%20-%20the%201%2C000th%20day%20of%20conflict.%20Sweden%2C%20Finland%2C%20Norway%20and%20Denmark%20have%20issued%20advisories%20that%20ask%20citizens%20to%20make%20sure%20they%20sustain%20themselves%20in%20case%20of%20a%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Sweden%20started%20sending%20out%20millions%20of%20pamphlets%20on%20Monday%20that%20contained%20information%20about%20how%20to%20prepare%20for%20war%2C%20natural%20disasters%20and%20cyber%20or%20terror%20attacks%2C%20Finland%20launched%20a%20website%20gathering%20information%20on%20preparedness%20for%20different%20crises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Swedish%20pamphlet%20says%3A%20%26quot%3BMilitary%20threat%20levels%20are%20increasing.%20We%20must%20be%20prepared%20for%20the%20worst-case%20scenario%20--%20an%20armed%20attack%20on%20Sweden%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2032-page%20booklet%20'If%20Crisis%20Or%20War%20Comes'%20contains%20tips%20such%20as%20stocking%20up%20on%20non-perishable%20food%20and%20water%2C%20keeping%20cash%20on%20hand%20and%20growing%20fruit%20and%20vegetables%20in%20gardens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Sweden%20is%20attacked%20by%20another%20country%2C%20we%20will%20never%20give%20up.%20All%20information%20to%20the%20effect%20that%20resistance%20is%20to%20cease%20is%20false%2C%26quot%3B%20reads%20a%20line%20in%20the%20booklet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20an%20updated%20version%20of%20a%20pamphlet%20that%20Sweden%20has%20issued%20five%20times%20since%20World%20War%20II.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20version%20doesn't%20mention%20Russia%2C%20Ukraine%20or%20any%20other%20country%20by%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brochure%20is%20available%20in%20print%20in%20both%20Swedish%20and%20English%20and%20digital%20versions%20are%20available%20in%20several%20other%20languages%20--%20including%20Arabic%2C%20Farsi%2C%20Ukrainian%2C%20Polish%2C%20Somali%20and%20Finnish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinland's%20website%20asserts%20authorities%20are%20%26quot%3Bwell%20prepared%20for%20self-defence%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20shares%20a%201%2C340-kilometre%20border%20with%20Russia%20and%20it%20has%20maintained%20a%20higher%20level%20of%20preparedness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Moscow's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20Finland%20announced%20plans%20to%20build%20a%20200-kilometre%20border%20fence%20-%2010%20feet%20tall%20and%20topped%20with%20barbed%20wire%20-%20with%20Russia%20which%20is%20due%20to%20be%20completed%20by%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Swedish%20and%20Finnish%20checklists%20include%20easy-to-cook%20food.%20Finland%20has%20also%20asked%20its%20citizens%20to%20arrange%20for%20a%20backup%20power%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Norway%20has%20urged%20its%20citizens%20to%20be%20prepared%20to%20manage%20on%20their%20own%20for%20a%20week%20in%20the%20event%20of%20war%20and%20other%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20sent%20out%202.2%20million%20paper%20copies%2C%20one%20for%20each%20household%20in%20Norway%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcjr4zwj2lgdo%5C%22%3EBBC%20quoted%20Tore%20Kamfjord%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20responsible%20for%20the%20campaign%20of%20self-preparedness%20at%20the%20Norwegian%20Directorate%20for%20Civil%20Protection%20(DSB)%2C%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETins%20of%20beans%2C%20energy%20bars%2C%20pasta%2C%20and%20medicines%20-%20including%20iodine%20tablets%20in%20case%20of%20a%20nuclear%20accident%20-%20are%20included%20in%20the%20list%20of%20items%20to%20be%20kept%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nordic%20neighbours%20Sweden%20and%20Finland%20dropped%20decades%20of%20military%20non-alignment%20to%20join%20the%20US-led%20defence%20alliance%20NATO%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Russia's%202022%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%20Norway%20was%20a%20founding%20member%20of%20the%20Western%20defensive%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDenmark's%20emergency%20management%20agency%2C%20as%20per%20a%20BBC%20report%2C%20emailed%20its%20citizens%20details%20on%20the%20water%2C%20food%20and%20medicine%20they%20would%20need%20to%20get%20through%20a%20crisis%20for%20three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Vladimir%20Putin%20eased%20Russia's%20rules%20for%20nuclear%20strikes%20days%20after%20the%20US%20allowed%20Ukraine%20to%20fire%20long-range%20American-made%20missiles%20into%20Russian%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwenty-three%20of%20the%2032%20NATO%20members%20-%20up%20from%20just%20three%20a%20decade%20ago%20-%20have%20now%20agreed%20to%20reach%20the%20target%20of%20spending%20two%20per%20cent%20of%20gross%20domestic%20product%20on%20defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20growing%20consensus%2C%20however%2C%20is%20that%20Europe%20will%20have%20to%20do%20more%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20can%20stand%20on%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A173204