ection%20Certificate%20(NOC)%2C%20at%20no-cost%20to%20the%20government%2C%20from%20the%20sports%20ministry%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20tournament%20but%20apparently%20couldn't%20get%20clearance%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA).%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20told%20unofficially%20that%20the%20blind%20team%20will%20not%20be%20permitted%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan.%20We%20were%20scheduled%20to%20travel%20to%20Wagah%20border%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20as%20of%20now%2C%20no%20clearance%20has%20come%20from%20the%20ministry%20officials.%20So%2C%20we%20are%20a%20bit%20disappointed%2C%26quot%3B%20Shailendra%20Yadav%2C%20General%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Cricket%20Association%20for%20the%20Blind%20in%20India%20(CABI)%2C%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20said%20that%20the%20decision%20could%20have%20been%20conveyed%20to%20the%20team%20a%20tad%20earlier%20so%20that%20they%20could%20have%20spared%20of%20the%20efforts%20to%20pick%20the%20team%20from%20a%20selection%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20saying%20when%20the%20mainstream%20cricket%20team%20is%20not%20safe%20how%20can%20you%20be%20safe%20there.%20Of%20course%2C%20we%20will%20accept%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20why%20hold%20the%20decision%20till%20the%20last%20minute%2C%20why%20not%20inform%20us%20a%20month%20or%2025%20days%20back.%20There%20is%20a%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yadav%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20blind%20cricket%20is%20currently%20staying%20back%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20where%20they%20had%20conducted%20a%2025-day%20training%20camp%20before%20selecting%20the%20World%20Cup%20squad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20also%20be%20mentioned%20that%20the%20government%20has%20not%20given%20clearance%20to%20the%20Indian%20national%20cricket%20team%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20next%20year's%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BCCI%20had%20informed%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20about%20India's%20inability%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20and%20the%20global%20governing%20body%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20passed%20the%20information%20to%20the%20PCB.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20talks%20are%20on%20about%20a%20possible%20%E2%80%98Hybrid%20Model'%2C%20the%20PCB%20is%20yet%20to%20agree%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Yadav%20said%20the%20CABI%20has%20kept%20all%20the%20communication%20channels%20with%20the%20government%20officials%20open%2C%20hoping%20for%20a%20reversal%20of%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20still%20communicating%20with%20the%20ministry%20while%20staying%20back%20at%20New%20Delhi.%20Hopefully%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20favourable%20decision%2C%20even%20at%20the%20last%20minute%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20Blind%20Cricket%20Council%20had%20last%20week%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20whether%20India%20sends%20its%20team%20to%20Pakistan%20or%20not%20for%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20the%20event%20will%20go%20ahead%20on%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPakistan%20will%20be%20hosting%20the%20event%20on%20schedule%20and%20it%20makes%20no%20difference%20whether%20the%20Indian%20team%20comes%20or%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chairman%20Syed%20Sultan%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20said%20all%20arrangements%20for%20hosting%20the%20World%20Cup%20had%20been%20completed%20by%20the%20PBCC%20and%20there%20would%20be%20no%20change%20to%20the%20schedule%20at%20all.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732035360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F8k1siva_blind-cricket-_640x480_12_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Findian-blind-cricket-team-to-not-travel-to-pakistan-for-t20-world-cup-reason-is-7057954%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20blind%20cricket%20team%20will%20not%20compete%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20as%20the%20government%20has%20denied%20it%20permission%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%2