aine%2C%20after%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20administration%20approved%20Kyiv's%20limited%20use%20of%20the%20weapons%20to%20hit%20targets%20inside%20Russia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Ukrainian%20media%20reports%2C%20the%20strike%20targeted%20a%20Russian%20military%20facility%20near%20the%20city%20of%20Karachev%20in%20the%20Bryansk%20region%2C%20located%20approximately%20130%20kilometres%20from%20the%20Ukrainian%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndeed%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20we%20used%20ATACMS%20to%20strike%20Russian%20territory.%20The%20strike%20was%20carried%20out%20against%20a%20facility%20in%20the%20Bryansk%20region%2C%20and%20it%20was%20successfully%20hit%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20Follow%2C%20No%20Index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsukraine.rbc.ua%2Fnews%2Fukraine-strikes-russian-territory-with-atacms-1732011994.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ukraine%20reported%2C%20citing%20an%20official%20in%20the%20nation's%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20was%20reportedly%20carried%20out%20on%20the%20night%20of%20November%2019%2C%20at%20the%2067th%20Arsenal%20of%20the%20Main%20Missile%20and%20Artillery%20Directorate%20of%20the%20Russian%20Ministry%20of%20Defense.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20General%20Staff%20also%20confirmed%20the%20attack%20on%20a%20facility%20near%20Karachev%20but%20did%20not%20comment%20on%20what%20missiles%20were%20used%2C%20saying%20the%20information%20is%20classified.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETill%20now%2C%20Ukraine%20has%20been%20using%20its%20homemade%20drones%20to%20attack%20deep%20into%20Russia%2C%20but%20the%20use%20of%20US%20weapons%20would%20be%20more%20destructive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20Confirms%20Use%20Of%20ATACMS%20Missile%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20on%20Tuesday%20confirmed%20that%20Ukraine%20used%20the%20long-range%20ATACMS%20missiles%20against%20its%20territory%20and%20said%20it%20marked%20a%20%26quot%3Bnew%20phase%20of%20the%20Western%20war%26quot%3B%20against%20Moscow%2C%20and%20vowed%20to%20react%20%26quot%3Baccordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20a%20signal%20that%20they%20want%20to%20escalate%2C%26quot%3B%20Russian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Sergei%20Lavrov%2C%20speaking%20at%20a%20G20%20press%20conference%20in%20Brazil%2C%20said%20of%20the%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20be%20taking%20this%20as%20a%20qualitatively%20new%20phase%20of%20the%20Western%20war%20against%20Russia.%20And%20we%20will%20react%20accordingly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20accusing%20Washington%20of%20helping%20Kyiv%20operate%20the%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELavrov%20also%20urged%20the%20West%20to%20read%20a%20decree%20signed%20by%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20lowers%20the%20threshold%20for%20when%20Moscow%20can%20use%20nuclear%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20that%20they%20will%20read%20this%20doctrine...%20in%20its%20entirety%2C%26quot%3B%20Lavrov%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20quoting%20Russian%20air%20defence%20forces%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20Follow%2C%20No%20Index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F11%2F19%2Feurope%2Fukraine-russia-atacms-biden-strike-intl%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20Russia%20shot%20down%20five%20of%20the%20six%20missiles%20fired%20by%20Ukraine%2C%20while%20another%20was%20damaged.%20Fragments%20from%20the%20damaged%20weapon%20reportedly%20fell%20on%20the%20territory%20of%20a%20military%20facility%2C%20causing%20a%20fire%20that%20has%20since%20been%20extinguished.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20reportedly%20no%20casualties%20or%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERussia's%20Responds%20To%20Biden's%20Missile%20Approval%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20on%20Tuesday%20approved%20an%20updated%20nuclear%20d