with%20his%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20long%20asserted%20that%20the%20Army%20Tactical%20Missile%20System%2C%20known%20by%20its%20initials%20ATACMS%2C%20is%20programmed%20by%20US%20specialists%20and%20requires%20guidance%20from%20American%20satellites.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732031940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fe2turnh_atacms-missile_625x300_19_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fin-a-first-ukraine-hits-russia-with-long-range-missile-after-bidens-approval-report-7057225%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ukrainian%20defence%20forces%20reportedly%20carried%20out%20their%20first%20strike%20in%20the%20border%20regions%20within%20Russian%20territory%20using%20Western-supplied%20ATACMS%20ballistic%20missiles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fin-a-first-ukraine-hits-russia-with-long-range-missile-after-bidens-approval-report-7057225%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jimmy%20Kimmel%20says%20'JD%20Vance%20must%20be%20on%2Fin%20his%20couch'%20as%20Trump%20enjoys%20boys'%20night%20out%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732031539000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115458664%2Cimgsize-1324176.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjimmy-kimmel-says-jd-vance-must-be-on%2Fin-his-couch-as-trump-enjoys-boys-night-out%2Farticleshow%2F115458561.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F115458561.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EJimmy%20Kimmel%20poked%20fun%20at%20Donald%20Trump's%20recent%20activities%2C%20from%20his%20cabinet%20picks%20to%20his%20'boys%20night%20out'%20at%20a%20UFC%20event.%20Kimmel%20joked%20about%20Trump's%20apparent%20'sub