s-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fnorways-crown-princesss-son-marius-borg-hiby-arrested-on-rape-suspicion%2Famp_articleshow%2F115457481.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fnorways-crown-princesss-son-marius-borg-hiby-arrested-on-rape-suspicion%2Famp_articleshow%2F115457481.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India-China%20Ties%20At%20%26quot%3BNew%20Starting%20Point%26quot%3B%3A%20Beijing%20After%20Ministers'%20Meeting%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20big%20step%20forward%20in%20India-China%20ties%2C%20the%20two%20countries%20have%20discussed%20resuming%20direct%20flights%20between%20the%20countries%20as%20well%20restarting%20the%20Kailash%20Mansarovar%20yatra.%20The%20Chinese%20foreign%20ministry%20has%20also%20said%20that%20the%20India-China%20relationship%20is%20at%20a%20%26quot%3Bnew%20starting%20point%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20key%20issues%20were%20discussed%20when%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20met%20his%20Chinese%20counterpart%20Wang%20Yi%20in%20Brazil's%20Rio%20de%20Janeiro%2C%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20G20%20Summit%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20was%20the%20first%20high-level%20engagement%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20since%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20disengagement%20process%20in%20the%20two%20contentious%20areas%20of%20Depsang%20and%20Demchok%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%20and%20the%20ministers%20noted%20that%20this%20had%20contributed%20to%20the%20maintenance%20of%20peace%20and%20tranquility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirect%20flights%20between%20India%20and%20China%20were%20suspended%20because%20of%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%20in%202020%20and%20have%20not%20resumed%20since%20then%20despite%20the%20restrictions%20being%20lifted.%20The%20stand-off%20in%20Ladakh%20began%20in%20May%20that%20year%20and%20a%20clash%20took%20place%20in%20Ladakh's%20Galwan%20the%20next%20month%20in%20which%2020%20Indian%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20in%20action%20and%20the%20Chinese%20side%20also%20suffered%20losses%2C%20with%20the%20exact%20number%20remaining%20unconfirmed.%20A%20troop%20buildup%20followed%20on%20both%20sides%20and%20military-level%20talks%20began%20taking%20place%20to%20resolve%20the%20stand-off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kailash%20Mansarovar%20pilgrimage%20to%20Mount%20Kailash%2C%20believed%20to%20be%20the%20abode%20of%20Lord%20Shiva%2C%20in%20China%20was%20also%20suspended%20during%20the%20pandemic%20in%202020%20and%20is%20yet%20to%20resume.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20note%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20said%20the%20resumption%20of%20the%20flights%20and%20the%20pilgrimage%20as%20well%20as%20data%20sharing%20on%20trans-border%20rivers%20and%20media%20exchanges%20were%20discussed%20by%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20and%20Mr%20Yi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Differences%20And%20Convergences'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20met%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20BRICS%20summit%20in%20Russia%20last%20month%2C%20after%20the%20disengagement%20in%20the%20two%20points%20was%20announced.%20The%20MEA%20said%20that%2C%20during%20the%20meeting%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20noted%20that%20India%20and%20China%20have%20both%20%26quot%3Bdifferences%20and%20convergences%26quot%3B%20and%20have%20worked%20constructively%20in%20the%20BRICS%20and%20the%20SCO%20(Shanghai%20Cooperation%20Organisation)%20framework%20while%20cooperating%20in%20G20%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsserting%20that%20India%20has%20had%20a%20consistent%20foreign%20policy%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20strongly%20committed%20to%20a%20multipolar%20world%2C%20including%20a%20multipolar%20Asia.%20Where%20India%20is%20concerned%2C%20its%20foreign%20policy%20has%20been%20principled%20and%20consistent%2C%20marked%20by%20independent%20thought%20and%20action.%20We%20are%20against%20unilateral%20approaches%20to%20establish%20dominance.%20India%20does%20not%20view%20its%20relationships%20through%20the%20prism%20of%20other%20nations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20said%20Chinese%20foreign%20minister%20Wang%20Yi%20agreed%20that%20India-China%20relations%20are%20very%20important%20for%20the%20world.%20Noting%20that%20PM%20Modi%20and%20President%20Jinping%20had%20discussed%20the%20way%20forward%2C%20the%20ministers%20felt%20the%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20stabilising%20ties%2C%20managing%20differences%20and%20taking%20the%20next%20steps%2C%20it%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Trust%20Through%20Dialogue'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20meeting%2C%20Chinese%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Lin%20Jian%20said%20China-India%20relations%20are%20at%20%26quot%3Ba%20new%20starting%20point%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20Foreign%20Minister%20Wang%20Yi%20noted%2C%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20held%20a%20successful%20meeting%20in%20Kazan%20not%20long%20ago.%20China-India%20relations%20are%20now%20at%20a%20new%20starting%20point.%20This%20serves%20the%20fundamental%20interests%20of%20the%20peoples%20of%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20meets%20the%20expectations%20of%20Global%20South%20countries%20and%20is%20in%20line%20with%20the%20trend%20of%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jian%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20two%20sides%20need%20to%20deliver%20on%20the%20important%20common%20understandings%20of%20the%20leaders%2C%20respect%20each%20other's%20core%20interests%20and%20major%20concerns%2C%20cement%20mutual%20trust%20through%20dialogue%20and%20communication%2C%20properly%20settle%20differences%20with%20sincerity%20and%20good%20faith%2C%20and%20bring%20the%20bilateral%20relations%20back%20to%20the%20track%20of%20stable%20and%20healthy%20development%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732028880000%2C%22v