0convenience%2C%20users%20can%20purchase%20digital%20tickets%20and%20mobile%20bus%20passes%20directly%20through%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECRUT%20has%20also%20pioneered%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20disaggregated%20ticketing%20system%20that%20collects%20passenger%20data%20by%20gender%2C%20age%2C%20and%20disability%20to%20enable%20more%20informed%20decision-making.%20This%20system%20identifies%20travel%20patterns%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20peak%20travel%20times%2C%20preferred%20modes%20of%20transport%2C%20and%20popular%20routes%20%E2%80%94%20allowing%20CRUT%20to%20tailor%20services%20to%20better%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20women%20and%20other%20demographics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20data%20can%20guide%20adjustments%20to%20bus%20schedules%2C%20increase%20frequency%20on%20popular%20routes%2C%20or%20assign%20female%20conductors%20for%20added%20safety%2C%20ensuring%20that%20public%20transport%20remains%20both%20responsive%20and%20inclusive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20city%20is%20also%20home%20to%20the%20Babasaheb%20Bhimrao%20Ambedkar%20Bus%20Terminal%20(BSABT)%2C%20connecting%20Odisha%20through%20both%20interstate%20and%20intrastate%20bus%20routes.%20With%2044%20bus%20bays%2C%20six%20city%20service%20bays%2C%20and%20parking%20for%20111%20buses%2C%20it%20accommodates%20over%2030%2C000%20passengers%20daily%2C%20making%20it%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20transport%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fitdp.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FMOBILIZE-BhubaneswarSTA2023-final.pdf%5C%22%3ESustainable%20Transport%20Award%20STA%202023%20Spotlight%3A%20Bhubaneswar%2C%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20for%20Institute%20for%20Transportation%20and%20Development%20Policy%2C%20Published%20in%20September%202023%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22