Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fhunter-biden-enjoys-family-day-at-disneyland-ahead-of-federal-sentencing%2Famp_articleshow%2F115456183.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fhunter-biden-enjoys-family-day-at-disneyland-ahead-of-federal-sentencing%2Famp_articleshow%2F115456183.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThere's%20A%20Photo...%26quot%3B%3A%20Manipur%20Chief%20Minister%20vs%20P%20Chidambaram%20On%20Militancy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EManipur%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20today%20blamed%20%26quot%3Bsome%20vested%20interests%26quot%3B%20for%20reigniting%20a%20new%20cycle%20of%20violence%20in%20the%20state%2C%20after%20having%20been%20relatively%20peaceful%20for%20three-four%20months%2C%20and%20criticised%20Congress%20leader%20P%20Chidambaram%20as%20someone%20who%20%26quot%3Bcreated%20the%20present%20crisis%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh's%20frontal%20attack%20came%20hours%20after%20Mr%20Chidambaram%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20suggested%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Meitei%2C%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20and%20the%20Naga%20can%20live%20together%20in%20one%20state%20only%20if%20they%20have%20genuine%20regional%20autonomy%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20blamed%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20for%20causing%20the%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chidambaram%2C%20however%2C%20removed%20the%20post%20after%20Manipur%20Congress%20chief%20Keisham%20Meghachandra%20requested%20him%20to%20delete%20it%20%2C%20amid%20the%20volatile%20situation%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlease%20delete%20this%20post.%20Manipur%20is%20in%20turmoil%20(sic)%20situation.%20It%20is%20very%20sensitive%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Meghachandra%20replied%20to%20Mr%20Chidambaram%2C%20a%20request%20that%20the%20Congress%20MP%20seemed%20to%20have%20accepted%20as%20the%20post%20no%20longer%20remained%20on%20his%20timeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chidambaram's%20comment%20is%20his%20personal%20observation%20and%20does%20not%20reflect%20the%20stand%20of%20the%20party%2C%20Congress%20leader%20and%20former%20Manipur%20Chief%20Minister%20O%20Ibobi%20Singh%20told%20reporters%20in%20Imphal%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EShri%20Okram%20Ibobi%2C%20CLP%20leader%20along%20with%20other%20party%20leaders%2C%20spoke%20to%20the%20press%20today%20in%20Imphal%20to%20clarify%20the%20position%20of%20the%20party%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20regional%20autonomy.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F0N8bytgvCI%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F0N8bytgvCI%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20A.%20Bimol%20Akoijam%20(%40Bimol_Akoijam)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBimol_Akoijam%2Fstatus%2F1858820779950968925%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2019%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20valley-dominant%20Meitei%20community%20has%20been%20seeking%20protection%20of%20Manipur's%20territorial%20integrity%2C%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20want%20a%20'separate%20administration'%20comprising%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20hill%20areas%20in%20southern%20Manipur%20which%20shares%20a%20border%20with%20Myanmar%20(and%20some%20areas%20in%20the%20north)%2C%20and%20the%20Nagas%20have%20had%20ambitions%20earlier%20to%20be%20united%20with%20all%20Naga-inhabited%20areas%20in%20the%20northeast%20region.%20The%20Kuki%20tribes%20share%20ethnic%20ties%20with%20people%20in%20Myanmar's%20Chin%20State%20and%20Mizoram%20-%20both%20Manipur's%20neighbours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20who%20has%20been%20battling%20ethnic%20fires%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-attack-on-hmar-village-in-manipurs-jiribam-by-suspected-meitei-militants-sparked-new-cycle-of-violence-7043146%5C%22%3Ea%20fresh%20cycle%20of%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20broke%20out%20in%20the%20state's%20Jiribam%20district%20that%20has%20so%20claimed%20over%2019%20lives%20including%20women%20and%20children%2C%20took%20strong%20exception%20to%20Mr%20Chidambaram's%20swipe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chidambaram%20was%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20under%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20government%20in%202008%20when%20he%20steered%20the%20highly%20controversial%20tripartite%20suspension%20of%20operations%20(SoO)%20agreement%20between%20over%20a%20dozen%20Kuki-Zo%20militant%20groups%20on%20one%20side%20and%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20state%20government%20on%20the%20other%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%20in%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal%20on%20Tuesday.%20The%20Congress%20was%20also%20in%20power%20in%20Manipur%20at%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20say%20it%20openly.%20When%20he%20(Mr%20Chidambaram)%20was%20the%20(Union)%20Home%20Minister%20in%20the%20then%20Congress%20government%2C%20here%20in%20Manipur%20(Congress's)%20O%20Ibobi%20was%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20During%20their%20time%2C%20they%20brought%20a%20Myanmarese%20foreigner%2C%20Mr%20Thanglianpau%20Guite%2C%20a%20Myanmar-born%20who%20himself%20admitted%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20he%20contested%20an%20election%20for%20MP%20in%20Myanmar.%20That%20person%20is%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Zomi%20Revolutionary%20Army%20(ZRA)%20based%20in%20Myanmar%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20surprised%20how%20Mr%20Chidambaram%20-%20there%20is%20a%20photograph%2C%20there%20is%20Chidambaram%2C%20then%20Union%20Home%20Minister%2C%20and%20here%20is%20Thanglianpau%20Guite%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Zomi%20Revolutionary%20Army%2C%20who%20is%20from%20Myanmar%20-%20they%20never%20cared%20about%20people%20from%20the%20northeast%2C%20about%20indigenous%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said%2C%20holding%20up%20an%20enlarged%20photo%20with%20a%20red%20circle%20on%20who%20Mr%20Singh%20said%20was%20Thanglianpau%20Guite%20seen%20shaking%20hands%20with%20Mr%20Chidambaram%20in%20a%20black%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fkao6k5i_p-chidambaram_625x300_19_November_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20present%20crisis%20is%20not%20an%20ethnic%20conflict.%20It%20is%20a%20problem%20of%20illegal%20immigration%20from%20Myanmar%20with%20drugs%20and%20them%20trying%20to%20control%20the%20indigenous%20people%20of%20Manipur%2C%20and%20in%20the%20entire%20northeast.%20I%20find%20it%20funny%20to%20see%20his%20(Mr%20Chidambaram's)%20comment.%20I%20want%20to%20remind%20him%2C%20with%20these%20photographs%2C%20why%20he%20allowed%20these%20foreigners%20to%20enter%20India%2C%20to%20enter%20Manipur%20and%20even%20sign%20suspension%20of%20operations%20agreement%20with%20underground%20groups%20of%20illegal%20immigrants%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Mr%20Chidambaram)%20and%20the%20Congress%20created%20the%20crisis.%20What%20we%20are%20facing%20today%20in%20Manipur%20is%20their%20creation.%20They%20cannot%20wash%20off%20their%20hands%20easily.%20People%20do%20understand%2C%20whatever%20is%20happening%20in%20Manipur%20is%20a%20chronic%20problem%20created%20by%20Congress%20and%20Chidambaram%20himself.%20Here%20are%20the%20photographs%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said%2C%20adding%20allegations%20and%20propaganda%20by%20national%20leaders%20should%20stop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20appeal%20to%20him%2C%20do%20not%20play%20more%20destructive%20games%20to%20destabilise%20Manipur%20and%20the%20entire%20northeast.%20Congress%20leaders%20should%20look%20at%20themselves%20that%20happened%20in%20Manipur%20during%20their%20time.%20How%20many%20were%20killed%20in%20fake%20encounters%3F%20There%20are%201%2C500%20cases%20of%20Manipur%20fake%20encounter%20cases%20