with-all-kuki-zo-insurgent-groups-manipur-assembly-in-unanimous-resolution-5150821%5C%22%3EEnd%20Ceasefire%20With%20All%20Kuki-Zo%20Insurgent%20Groups%3A%20Manipur%20Assembly%20Unanimous%20Resolution%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20assembly%20on%20February%2029%20unanimously%20passed%20a%20resolution%20asking%20the%20Centre%20to%20scrap%20the%20SoO%20agreement%20with%20some%2025%20Kuki-Zo%20insurgent%20groups.%20The%20deadline%20for%20extension%20of%20the%20SoO%20agreement%20ended%20the%20same%20day.%20Whether%20the%20SoO%20agreement%20has%20been%20renewed%20is%20not%20known.%20The%20deaths%20of%2010%20%26quot%3Bmilitants%26quot%3B%20in%20Manipur's%20Jiribam%20in%20an%20encounter%20with%20the%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20(CRPF)%20may%20give%20some%20clues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBroadly%2C%20the%20SoO%20agreement%20says%20the%20insurgents%20are%20to%20stay%20at%20designated%20camps%20and%20their%20weapons%20kept%20in%20locked%20storage%2C%20to%20be%20monitored%20regularly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fq6v4eko_manipur-insurgent-camp-soo_625x300_02_June_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20over%20two%20dozen%20Kuki-Zo%20insurgent%20groups%20come%20under%20two%20umbrella%20groups%20-%20the%20Kuki%20National%20Organisation%20(KNO)%2C%20and%20the%20United%20People's%20Front%20(UPF).%20These%20two%20representing%20the%20others%20have%20signed%20the%20SoO%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeitei%20leaders%20have%20alleged%20the%20SoO%20groups%20have%20been%20working%20to%20strengthen%20themselves%20over%20the%20years%20by%20taking%20advantage%20of%20the%20ceasefire%2C%20until%20a%20time%20came%20to%20engineer%20a%20violent%20attack%20for%20a%20separate%20land.%20Geopolitical%20analysts%20have%20speculated%20the%20Kuki%20armed%20groups%20we