r%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffsii.in%2Fimportance-of-seed-banks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EImportance%20of%20Seed%20Banks%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Federation%20of%20Seed%20Industry%20of%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732024705000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-2-1732015773.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D381089%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Darlapudi%20Ravi%20was%20an%20assistant%20general%20manager%20at%20a%20cement%20industry%20when%20he%20realised%20how%20modern%20dietary%20practices%20lead%20to%20a%20variety%20of%20diseases.%20Here's%20how%20this%20realisation%20motivated%20him%20to%20build%20a%20seed%20bank.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F381089%2Fseed-preservation-andhra-pradesh-darlapudi-ravi-indigenous-local-varieties%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sharad%20Pawar%20Rubbished%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Attack%20On%20Adani%3A%20BJP's%20Amit%20Malviya%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESharad%20Pawar's%20remarks%20about%20the%20Dharavi%20Redevelopment%20Project%20exposes%20the%20lies%20of%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%2C%20the%20BJP's%20Amit%20Malviya%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20today.%20Mr%20Pawar's%20remarks%2C%20make%20it%20clear%20that%20%26quot%3BUddhav%20(Thackeray)%20and%20Rahul%20(Gandhi)%20had%20been%20lying%20all%20along%20to%20mislead%20Mumbai%20and%20Maharashtra%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20led%20MVA%2C%20which%20had%20signed%20off%20the%20Dharavi%20project%20to%20Adani%20Group%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20post%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20a%20%C2%A0digital%20platform%2C%20a%20clip%20of%20which%20was%20shared%20by%20Mr%20Malviya%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%2C%20the%20veteran%20leader%20of%20the%20MVA%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Dharavi%20issue%20is%20not%20at%20all%20there.%20All%20these%20issues%20were%20attacking%20(Gautam)%20Adani.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdani%20was%20not%20interested%20in%20Dharavi%20when%20this%20meeting%20took%20place.%20In%20fact%2C%20Dharavi%20project%20was%20given%20to%20some%20other%20people.%20They%20have%20come%20here.%20Some%20negotiations%20are%20on%20but%20not%20with%20Adani%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSharad%20Pawar%20rubbishes%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20attack%20on%20Adani.%20He%20further%20adds%20that%20Adani%20was%20not%20interested%20in%20Dharavi%20Redevelopment%20project.%20This%2C%20coming%20from%20the%20senior%20most%20politician%20in%20the%20MVA%20camp%2C%20just%20before%20the%20crucial%20polling%2C%20is%20embarrassing%20for%20the%20alliance%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Malviya%20wrote%20in%20his%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Dharavi%20Redevelopment%20project%20-%20a%20joint%20venture%20between%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20and%20the%20Adani%20Group%20that%20is%20set%20to%20give%20a%20facelift%20to%20the%20largest%20slum%20in%20Asia%20-%20has%20been%20hot-button%20issue%20for%20the%20assembly%20election%20in%20Maharashtra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%20have%20raised%20concerns%20about%20transparency%20in%20the%20awarding%20of%20the%20contract%20by%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20in%202022.%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20UBT%2C%20has%20said%20the%20matter%20concerns%20the%20whole%20of%20Mumbai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDharavi%20--%20which%20has%20a%20diverse%20population%20and%20reflects%20the%20cosmopolitan%20spirit%20of%20Mumbai%20--%20has%20been%20a%20Congress%20stronghold%20for%20two%20decades.%20This%20year%2C%20it%20will%20see%20a%20fight%20between%20Congress's%20Dr%20Jyoti%20Gaikwad%2C%20sister%20of%20Varsha%20Gaikwad%20who%20represented%20it%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20since%202004%2C%20and%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena's%20Rajesh%20Khandare.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732023540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fmeusqr88_-sharad-pawar_625x300_20_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsharad-pawar-exposes-uddhav-thackeray-rahul-gandhis-lies-on-dharavi-amit-malviya-7056786%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sharad%20Pawar's%20remarks%20about%20the%20Dharavi%20Redevelopment%20Project%20exposes%20the%20lies%20of%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%2C%20the%20BJP's%20Amit%20Malviya%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsharad-pawar-exposes-uddhav-thackeray-rahul-gandhis-lies-on-dharavi-amit-malviya-7056786%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%2C%20China%20Direct%20Flights%20Soon%3F%20S%20Jaishankar%20Meets%20Chinese%20Foreign%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20big%20step%20forward%20in%20India-China%20ties%2C%20the%20two%20countries%20have%20discussed%20resuming%20direct%20flights%20between%20the%20countries%20as%20well%20restarting%20the%20Kailash%20Mansarovar%20yatra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20key%20issues%20were%20discussed%20when%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20met%20his%20Chinese%20counterpart%20Wang%20Yi%20in%20Rio%20de%20Janeiro%2C%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20G20%20Summit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20was%20the%20first%20high-level%20engagement%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20since%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20disengagement%20process%20in%20the%20two%20contentious%20areas%20of%20Depsang%20and%20Demchok%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%20and%20the%20ministers%20noted%20that%20this%20had%20contributed%20to%20the%20maintenance%20of%20peace%20and%20tranquility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirect%20flights%20between%20India%20and%20China%20were%20suspended%20because%20of%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%20in%202020%20and%20have%20not%20resumed%20since%20then%20despite%20the%20restrictions%20being%20lifted.%20The%20stand-off%20in%20Ladakh%20began%20in%20May%20that%20year%20and%20a%20clash%20took%20place%20in%20Ladakh's%20Galwan%20the%20next%20month%20in%20which%2020%20Indian%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20in%20action%20and%20the%20Chinese%20side%20also%20suffered%20losses%2C%20with%20the%20exact%20number%20remaining%20unconfirmed.%20A%20troop%20buildup%20followed%20on%20both%20sides%20and%20military-level%20talks%20began%20taking%20place%20to%20resolve%20the%20stand-off.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732023420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fd55j109_s-jaishankar-x_625x300_19_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-china-direct-flights-soon-s-jaishankar-meets-chinese-foreign-minister-7056588%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20big%20step%20forward%20in%20India-China%20ties%2C%20the%20two%20countries%20have%20discussed%20resuming%20direct%20flights%20between%20the%20countries%20as%20well%20restarting%20the%20Kailash%20Mansarovar%20yatra.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-china-direct-flights-soon-s-jaishankar-meets-chinese-foreign-minister-7056588%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Travel%20Diaries%3A%20Will%20'Adivasi%20Asmita'%20Decide%20Jharkhand%20Elections%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F2h90u2qo_jharkhand-assembly_640x480_13_November_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJharkhand%20is%20set%20to%20vote%20for%2038%20seats%20in%20the%20second%20and%20final%20phase%20of%20assembly%20elections%20on%20November%2020%2C%20alongside%20Maharashtra.%20In%20the%20first%20phase%2C%20held%20on%20November%2013%2C%20the%20state%20voted%20for%2043%20seats%2C%20primarily%20in%20Kolhan%20(14)%2C%20South%20Chotanagpur%20(15)%2C%20Palamu%20(9)%2C%20and%20a%20few%20seats%20in%20North%20Chotanagpur%20(5).%20In%20the%20second%20phase%2C%2020%20seats%20in%20North%20Chotanagpur%20and%2018%20in%20Santhal%20Pargana%20will%20go%20to%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20bloc%20aims%20to%20retain%20power%2C%20buoyed%20by%20its%20welfare%20schemes%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Eadivasi%20asmita%3C%2Fem%3E%20(tribal%20pride)%20narrative.%20The%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20hopes%20to%20make%20a%20comeback%2C%20capitalising%20on%20allegations%20of%20non-performance%20and%20corruption%20against%20the%20Soren%20government.%20In%20the%20first%20phase%2C%20women%20voters%20outnumbered%20men%20by%204.8%25.%20In%20fact%2C%2037%20of%20the%2043%20constituencies%20saw%20higher%20female%20voter%20turnout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhase%201%20of%20polling%20in%20Jharkhand%20recorded%20a%20voter%20turnout%20of%2066.65%25%2C%20a%202.75%20percentage%20point%20increase%20from%20the%202019%20elections.%20Male%20voter%20turnout%20stood%20at%2064.27%25%2C%20while%20female%20turnout%20was%2069.04%25.%20The%20INDIA%20bloc%20has%20hailed%20the%20high%20turnout%2C%20claiming%20that%20women%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20Maiyya%20Samman%20Yojana%20turned%20out%20in%20large%20numbers%2C%20giving%20them%20an%20edge.%20The%20NDA%2C%20however%2C%20attributes%20the%20high%20turnout%20to%20anti-incumbency%20sentiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20travelled%20through%20the%20state%20during%20Diwali%20and%20Chhath%20Puja%20and%20below%20are%20my%20findings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdivasi%20'Asmita'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arrest%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren%20has%20reignited%20the%20%3Cem%3Eadivasi%20asmita%3C%2Fem%3E%20(tribal%20pride)%20issue.%20In%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20tribals%20overwhelmingly%20voted%20against%20the%20NDA%2C%20with%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20winning%20all%20five%20ST-reserved%20seats.%20The%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20(JMM)%20has%20successfully%20framed%20the%20narrative%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20jailed%20their%20popular%20Chief%20Minister%20as%20part%20of%20a%20political%20conspiracy.%20Hemant%20Soren%20has%20positioned%20himself%20as%20the%20preeminent%20tribal%20leader%20in%20Jharkhand.%20In%20response%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20attempting%20to%20consolidate%20a%20coalition%20of%20tribal%20leaders%2C%20including%20Babulal%20Marandi%2C%20Arjun%20Munda%2C%20and%20Champai%20Soren%2C%20to%20counter%20Hemant%20and%20showcase%20its%20own%20tribal%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EInsider%20vs%20Outsider%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20elections%20have%20turned%20into%20a%20battle%20between%20locals%20and%20outsiders.%20Tribals%20are%20economically%20disadvantaged%2C%20while%20outsiders%20occupy%20most%20government%20and%20private%20sector%20jobs%20and%20are%20generally%20more%20prosperous.%20Tribals%20accuse%20outsiders%20of%20seizing%20their%20land%20and%20prospering%20at%20their%20expense.%20The%20JMM%20is%20viewed%20as%20the%20party%20representing%20local%20interests%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20is%20seen%20as%20representing%20the%20outsiders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Identity%20Battle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lines%20of%20identity%20have%20become%20so%20sharply%20drawn%20that%20voters%20seem%20less%20concerned%20about%20the%20performance%20of%20their%20elected%20representatives.%20Despite%20extensive%20media%20debates%20on%20issues%20like%20anti-incumbency%20and%20MLA%20performance%2C%20I%20found%20that%20local%20voters%20were%20generally%20indifferent%20to%20these%20concerns%2C%20provided%20the%20MLA%20belonged%20to%20their%20caste%20or%20community.%20When%20I%20probed%20one%20local%20about%20the%20performance%20of%20their%20MLA%2C%20he%20responded%20by%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Ekaam%20kaun%20karta%20hai%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20(Who%20works%2C%20after%20all%3F)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP's%20Slogan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20adopted%20the%20slogan%20'Batenge%20to%20Katenge'%20(divided%20we%20fall)%2C%20which%20has%20polarised%20the%20election.%20Jharkhand%20has%20a%20Muslim%20population%20of%2014.5%25%20(as%20per%20the%202011%20census)%2C%20which%20is%20roughly%20equal%20to%20the%20national%20average.%20The%20BJP%20has%20raised%20concerns%20over%20issues%20like%20'love%20jihad'%2C%20accusing%20Muslim%20men%20of%20marrying%20tribal%20women%20and%20subsequently%20taking%20control%20of%20tribal%20land%20and%20local%20governance%20through%20tribal%20%3Cem%3Esarpanchs%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20BJP%20has%20particularly%20emphasised%20this%20issue%20in%20Santhal%20Pargana%2C%20accusing%20the%20JMM%20of%20failing%20to%20prevent%20the%20infiltration%20of%20outsiders%2C%20which%20they%20claim%20has%20altered%20the%20region's%20demographic%20makeup.%20The%20party%20has%20promised%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20and%20hopes%20to%20make%20inroads%20in%20the%20region%20that%20was%20swept%20by%20the%20JMM-Congress-Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20alliance%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%20A%20Weak%20Link%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20won%2016%20seats%2C%20mostly%20in%20the%20Chotanagpur%20division.%20The%20party%20has%20traditional%20strongholds%20in%20this%20region%2C%20although%2C%20over%20the%20years%2C%20many%20of%20these%20have%20shifted%20to%20the%20BJP.%20Just%20days%20before%20the%20polls%2C%20the%20Congress%20replaced%20its%20state%20president%2C%20Rajesh%20Thakur%2C%20who%20had%20made%20significant%20efforts%20to%20rebuild%20the%20party's%20organisation.%20The%20Congress%20is%20contesting%2037%20seats%20in%20this%20election%2C%20but%20many%20view%20it%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bweak%20link%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERise%20Of%20Kalpana%20Soren%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arrest%20of%20Hemant%20Soren%20propelled%20Kalpana%20Soren%20into%20the%20spotlight%20within%20the%20JMM.%20She%20took%20charge%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20campaign%20and%20became%20its%20star%20campaigner%2C%20connecting%20with%20women%20and%20young%20voters%20and%20energising%20the%20party%20cadre.%20Kalpana's%20rallies%20often%20attract%20large%20crowds%20of%20tribal%20women%2C%20who%20relate%20to%20her%20discussions%20about%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20Maiya%20Samman%20Yojana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESchemes%20On%20Offer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Soren%20government%20launched%20the%20Maiya%20Samman%20Yojana%2C%20modelled%20on%20the%20Laadli%20Bahin%20Yojana.%20Under%20this%20scheme%2C%20the%20government%20provides%20Rs%201%2C000%20per%20month%20to%2050%20lakh%20women.%20Women%20voters%20are%20becoming%20an%20increasingly%20important%20demographic%2C%20and%20are%20playing%20a%20decisive%20role%20in%20elections.%20The%20BJP's%20manifesto%20also%20includes%20the%20Go%20Go%20Yojana%2C%20while%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20has%20promised%20to%20increase%20the%20cash%20dole%20in%20its%20manifesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERise%20Of%20The%20Tiger%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20Jairam%20Mahato%20has%20shaken%20up%20Jharkhand%20politics.%20As%20a%20Kurmi%20leader%2C%20he%20has%20reignited%20the%20'insider%20vs%20outsider'%20debate%20by%20demanding%20that%20the%201932%20land%20records%20be%20used%20as%20the%20basis%20for%20the%20domicile%20policy.%20His%20rallies%20draw%20large%20crowds%2C%20particularly%20among%20the%20youth%2C%20and%20he%20has%20significantly%20impacted%20the%20INDIA%20bloc's%20prospects%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20In%20the%20assembly%20polls%2C%20he%20could%20pose%20a%20challenge%20to%20the%20All%20Jharkhand%20Students%20Union%20(AJSU)%2C%20a%20party%20that%20also%20represents%20Kurmis%20and%20has%20been%20pushing%20for%20their%20inclusion%20in%20the%20ST%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBread%20And%20Butter%20Issues%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERising%20prices%2C%20unemployment%2C%20and%20rural%20distress%20remain%20key%20issues%20in%20the%20state.%20Jharkhand%20is%20one%20of%20India's%20most%20backward%20states%2C%20with%20many%20of%20its%20districts%20ranked%20among%20the%20250%20most%20backward%20in%20the%20country.%20Its%20per%20capita%20income%20is%20roughly%20half%20the%20national%20average.%20Although%20Jharkhand%20is%20rich%20in%20minerals%2C%20illegal%20mining%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20industrial%20development%E2%80%94exacerbated%20by%20its%20landlocked%20nature%E2%80%94have%20hindered%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBattle%20Of%20Alliances%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20aligned%20with%20the%20AJSU%2C%20the%20Jharkhand%20Vikas%20Morcha%20(JVM)%2C%20and%20the%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(LJP)%2C%20while%20the%20JMM%20has%20partnered%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20RJD%20and%20Left%20parties.%20Seamless%20vote%20transfer%20between%20alliance%20partners%20will%20be%20crucial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20AJSU%20contested%20separately%2C%20leading%20to%20their%20defeat.%20Had%20they%20contested%20together%2C%20they%20could%20have%20won%2041%20of%20the%2081%20seats%2C%20securing%20a%20simple%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20an%20average%20of%2015%20candidates%20in%20each%20constituency%2C%20and%20independents%20or%20smaller%20parties%20could%20play%20the%20role%20of%20spoilers.%20Micro-management%20and%20voter%20mobilisation%20could%20ultimately%20decide%20the%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732023120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F2h90u2qo_jharkhand-assembly_640x480_13_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ftravel-diaries-will-adivasi-asmita-decide-jharkhand-elections-7056688%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20INDIA%20bloc%20aims%20to%20retain%20power%2C%20buoyed%20by%20its%20welfare%20schemes%20and%20the%20adivasi%20asmita%20(tribal%20pride)%20narrative.%20The%20NDA%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20hopes%20to%20make%20a%20comeback%20by%20capitalizing%20on%20allegations%20of%20corruption%20against%20the%20Soren%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ftravel-diaries-will-adivasi-asmita-decide-jharkhand-elections-7056688%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Class%2012%20Student%20Builds%20Solar-Powered%20Agro%20Vehicle%20With%20Zero%20Carbon%20Emission%20for%20Farmers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20tender%20age%20of%2017%2C%20Suhani%20Chauhan%2C%20a%20Class%2012%20student%20is%20making%20waves%20with%20a%20design%20that%20empower%20farmers%20by%20reducing%20production%20costs%20and%20boosting%20crop%20yields%2C%20helping%20them%20achieve%20greater%20efficiency%20and%20profitability%20in%20their%20farming%20practices.%20Her%20So-Apt%20Agro%20vehicle%20is%20an%20innovative%2C%20solar-powered%20farming%20vehicle%20that%20promises%20to%20be%20a%20boon%20for%20farmers%20with%20potential%20to%20cut%20down%20carbon%20emissions%20by%202%2C72%2C000%20metric%20tonnes.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuhani%20was%20a%20Class%207%20student%20when%20a%20school%20field%20trip%20to%20the%20farms%20of%20Manesar%20