20this%2C%20the%20organisation%20aims%20to%20balance%20policy%20regulations%20and%20citizen%20awareness%20perfectly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20National%20Building%20Code%20(NBC)%20has%20promising%20things%20included%20as%20construction%20guidelines%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gopal%2C%20who%20hopes%20to%20streamline%20and%20enhance%20their%20initiatives%20by%20learning%20from%20their%20past%20experiences%20and%20projects%20in%20the%20upcoming%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Beyond%20Carlton%20was%20successful%20in%20launching%20the%20%E2%80%98B-FIRE%20SAFE%E2%80%99%20initiative%20to%20sensitise%20citizens%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20fire%20safety%20in%20residential%20areas%20in%202021.%20This%20has%20improved%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20observe%2C%20assess%2C%20and%20act%20promptly%20during%20fire%20hazards%20in%20residential%20complexes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEstablishing%20fire%20safety%20in%20Odisha%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Beyond%20Carlton%20signed%20an%20MoU%20with%20the%20Odisha%20State%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority%20(OSDMA)%20to%20build%20a%20fire%20safety%20framework%20for%20the%20twin%20cities%20Bhubaneswar%20and%20Cuttack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20was%20happy%20when%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F370334%2Fsambit-kumar-das-founder-ek-asha-ngo-odisha-tribes-computers-english-maths-art-think-centers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOdisha%3C%2Fa%3E%20Government%20approached%20them%20for%20a%20blueprint.%20%E2%80%9CBeyond%20Carlton%20wants%20to%20be%20a%20force%20leading%20to%20positive%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Venkitachalam%3B%20their%20credible%20work%20has%20pushed%20other%20states%20to%20adopt%20a%20similar%20model.%20Today%2C%20their%20blueprint%20facilitates%20all%20cities%20in%20Odisha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20Odisha%20has%20experience%20handling