20long%20been%20labour-intensive%2C%20inefficient%2C%20and%20hazardous.%20Fishermen%20and%20farmers%20dive%20into%20deep%2C%20muddy%20ponds%20%E2%80%94%20often%20as%20deep%20as%20eight%20to%2012%20feet%20%E2%80%94%20for%20hours%20to%20collect%20the%20seeds%2C%20risking%20injuries%20and%20infections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecognising%20these%20issues%2C%20Dr%20Manoj%20Kumar%2C%20a%20senior%20scientist%20at%20the%20National%20Research%20Centre%20for%20Makhana%20(NRCM)%2C%20has%20figured%20out%20a%20way%20to%20turn%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20cultivation%20into%20a%20more%20sustainable%20and%20profitable%20agricultural%20practice%2C%20benefiting%20thousands%20of%20farmers%20in%20the%20region.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPerils%20of%20an%20inefficient%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%20%3C%2Fem%3Eharvesting%20process%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20generations%2C%20families%20like%20Phool%20Dev%20Shahni%E2%80%99s%20in%20Darbhanga%2C%20Bihar%2C%20have%20relied%20on%20traditional%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20farming%20methods.%20Shahni%20would%20spend%20seven%20to%20eight%20hours%20every%20day%20underwater%2C%20surfacing%20every%20eight%20to%2010%20minutes.%20Sharp%20thorns%20on%20the%20plants%20caused%20frequent%20cuts%2C%20while%20the%20muddy%20water%20led%20to%20skin%20infections.%20This%20backbreaking%20process%20discouraged%20younger%20generations%20from%20continuing%20the%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDBnvXxuseEh%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDBnvXxuseEh%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%