s%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlok%E2%80%99s%20gym%20in%20Siliguri%20recently%20hosted%20a%20fundraiser%20to%20support%20Chandrika%E2%80%99s%20work.%20The%20concept%20was%20simple%3A%20for%20every%20pull-up%20that%20a%20participant%20completed%20during%20the%20event%2C%20a%20small%20donation%20would%20be%20made%20towards%20Indie%20RTR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20give%20back%20to%20the%20community%20and%20raise%20awareness%20about%20the%20strays%20in%20the%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20Alok%20explains.%20%E2%80%9COur%20goal%20was%20modest%2C%20but%20we%20were%20pleasantly%20surprised%20with%20the%20response.%20The%20event%20was%20a%20success.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20event%20not%20only%20raised%20funds%20but%20also%20educated%20people%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20caring%20for%20street%20animals%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chandrika%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIntroducing%20QR%20codes%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20Chandrika%E2%80%99s%20work%20has%20become%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope%20for%20many%20street%20animals%20in%20the%20area.%20But%20even%20with%20the%20support%20of%20her%20husband%20and%20a%20handful%20of%20caregivers%2C%20the%20work%20can%20be%20overwhelming.%20To%20manage%20the%20increasing%20number%20of%20rescues%2C%20Chandrika%20introduced%20an%20innovative%20system%3A%20QR%20code%20collars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FtempImageOWO8XK-1731659274-500x855.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ever%20rescued%20dog%20is%20provided%20a%20collar%20with%20a%20QR%20code%20containing%20all%20their%20medical%20details%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FtempImageOWO8XK-1731659274-500x855.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FtempImageOWO8XK-1731659274-176x300.jpg%20176w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FtempImageOWO8XK-1731659274-768x1313.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FtempImageOWO8XK-1731659274-899x1536.jpg%20899w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FtempImageOWO8XK-1731659274-150x256.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FtempImageOWO8XK-1731659274.jpg%20936w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-380227%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22855%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EEvery%20rescued%20dog%20is%20provided%20a%20collar%20with%20a%20QR%20code%20containing%20all%20their%20medical%20details%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20came%20to%20me%20as%20a%20way%20to%20keep%20track%20of%20the%20animals%20we%20rescue%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20place%20QR%20codes%20on%20the%20dogs%20after%20they%E2%80%99ve%20been%20treated.%20When%20someone%20scans%20it%2C%20they%20can%20see%20the%20dog%E2%80%99s%20medical%20history%20and%20our%20contact%20information.%20It%20helps%20raise%20awareness%20and%20allows%20us%20to%20keep%20track%20of%20the%20animals%20we%20care%20for.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrika%20has%20also%20employed%20two%20women%20%E2%80%94%20Akriti%20Subba%20and%20Rakhi%20Gurung%20%E2%80%94%20to%20help%20her%20in%20her%20mission.%20%E2%80%9CI%20pay%20them%20a%20very%20modest%20salary.%20They%20are%20also%20die-hard%20animal%20lovers%20and%20have%20been%20incredibly%20supportive%2C%20reaching%20out%20to%20me%20to%20join%20the%20mission.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98If%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20love%20them%2C%20at%20least%20don%E2%80%99t%20hurt%20them%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrika%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20align%20with