d%20them%3B%20at%20least%20don%E2%80%99t%20hurt%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20Chandrika%20Yolmo%20Lama%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731675309000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FtempImagefPV9Zl-1731658252.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D380185%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20former%20educator%20turned%20full-time%20animal%20advocate%2C%20Chandrika%20Yolmo%20Lama%E2%80%99s%20tireless%20work%20has%20helped%20rescue%20over%20200%20stay%20dogs.%20Today%2C%20she%20walks%20eight%20kilometres%20every%20morning%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20all%20stray%20dogs%20in%20her%20locality.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Arunava%20Banerjee%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A51%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F380185%2Fsaving-stray-dogs-rescue-rehabilitation-and-sharing-success-stories%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Koodugal%20Nest%20Is%20Turning%20Chennai%E2%80%99s%20Schools%20Into%20Havens%20for%20Sparrows%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNature%20is%20giving%20everything%20to%20human%20beings%2C%20but%20we%20are%20not%20giving%20much%20back%20to%20nature%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mr%20Ganeshan%20D%2C%20founder%20of%20Koodugal%20Nest%20(Network%20for%20Environment%20Sustainability%20Trust).%20The%20Chennai-based%20NGO%20is%20playing%20a%20key%20role%20in%20boosting%20the%20sparrow%20population%20in%20the%20city%20through%20its%20unique%20efforts%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328099%2Fpunjab-man-in-faridkot-plants-trees-and-mud-nests-for-indigenous-birds%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enest%20conservation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20an%20agricultural%20background%20in%20a%20small%20village%20near%20Bengaluru%2C%20Ganeshan%20D%20has%20always%20held%20a%20deep%20love%20for%20nature%2C%20which%20evolved%20into%20a%20passionate%20commitment%20to%20environmental%20conservation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaneshan%E2%80%99s%20journey%20is%20rooted%20in%20a%20solid%20foundation%20of%20education%2C%20professional%20experience%2C%20and%20a%20deep%20commitment%20to%20giving%20back%20to%20nature.%20He%20has%20carved%20out%20a%20unique%20path%2C%20dedicating%20himself%20to%20making%20a%20meaningful%20impact%20through%20conservation%20efforts%2C%20with%20a%20particular%20focus%20on%20sparrow%20preservation%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F336408%2Fchennai-floods-solution-to-groundwater-restoration-rainwater-harvesting-ancient-system-tamil-nadu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewater%20manageme%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F336408%2Fchennai-floods-solution-to-groundwater-restoration-rainwater-harvesting-ancient-system-tamil-nadu%2F%5C%22%3Ent%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20waste%20reduction.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20interest%20in%20nature%20began%20in%20his%20early%20years.%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20childhood%2C%20I%20have%20always%20been%20fascinated%20by%20nature%20and%20deeply%20passionate%20about%20conserving%20sparrows%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ganeshan%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20As%20a%20student%2C%20his%20curiosity%20was%20nurtured%20by%20a%20supportive%20professor%20who%20recognised%20his%20zeal%20for%20the%20environment%20and%20encouraged%20him%20to%20pursue%20it%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20engineer%20to%20environment%20warrior%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaneshan%20pursued%20mechanical%20engineering%2C%20earning%20a%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20and%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree.%20Following%20his%20studies%2C%20he%20worked%20