em%20about%20sparrow%20conservation%20but%20also%20improves%20their%20motor%20skills%2C%20concentration%2C%20and%20empathy.%20These%20activities%20have%20significantly%20reduced%20screen%20time%20and%20have%20helped%20children%20develop%20a%20keen%20interest%20in%20the%20natural%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Ganeshan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20future%20plans%2C%20Ganeshan%20is%20determined%20to%20make%20sparrows%20a%20common%20sight%20across%20Chennai%20and%20expand%20the%20reach%20of%20the%20project%20to%20more%20schools%20and%20gated%20communities.%20%E2%80%9COur%20goal%20is%20to%20reach%201%2C00%2C000%20families%20and%20distribute%20more%20nest%20boxes%20in%2010%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NGO%20is%20also%20focusing%20on%20developing%20sparrow%20sanctuaries%20in%20more%20schools%2C%20where%20sparrows%20can%20nest%20and%20flourish%20in%20safe%2C%20protected%20environments.%20They%20have%20successfully%20established%20eight%20sparrow%20sanctuaries%20so%20far%2C%20providing%20a%20home%20for%20100%20to%20200%20sparrows%20on%20each%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20first%20partner%2C%20Dhanalakshmi%20Higher%20Secondary%20School%2C%20accepted%20fifteen%20boxes.%20Today%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20distributed%20over%2010%2C000.%20Initially%2C%20we%20aimed%20to%20install%201%2C000%20boxes%2C%20and%20we%20achieved%20that.%20Wherever%20we%E2%80%99ve%20distributed%20nest%20boxes%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20students%20get%20more%20engaged.%20I%E2%80%99m%20fortunate%20to%20have%20supportive%20parents%20who%20help%20me%20balance%20my%20work%20and%20the%20Koodugal%20project%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shanthini%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201040px)%20100vw%2C%201040px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-05-at-22.31.06-1-1731592372.jpeg%5C%22%20wi