0RBSK%E2%80%99s%20success.%20Such%20partnerships%20enhance%20the%20programme%E2%80%99s%20reach%2C%20strengthen%20service%20delivery%2C%20and%20amplify%20its%20impact.%20By%20joining%20forces%2C%20the%20Government%2C%20private%20sector%2C%20and%20civil%20society%20can%20share%20resources%2C%20expand%20healthcare%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20ensure%20that%20every%20child%20receives%20the%20essential%20care%20they%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHonouring%20a%2015-year-long%20commitment%20to%20children%E2%80%99s%20health%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20celebrate%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%2015th%20anniversary%20this%20year%2C%20we%20take%20stock%20of%20the%20path%20from%20our%20initial%20roots%20to%20our%20current%20extended%20paediatric%20care%20activities.%20Understanding%20that%20healthier%20children%20lead%20to%20healthier%20communities%20is%20the%20foundation%20of%20our%20commitment%20to%20children%E2%80%99s%20well-being.%20Beyond%20curing%20a%20disease%2C%20our%20focus%20on%20paediatric%20oncology%20demonstrates%20our%20commitment%20to%20justice%2C%20resilience%2C%20and%20hope%20in%20the%20face%20of%20adversity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20child%20whose%20life%20we%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20confirms%20our%20conviction%20that%20easily%20accessible%20healthcare%20has%20the%20capacity%20to%20change%20lives.%20As%20we%20strive%20towards%20a%20future%20where%20no%20kid%20battles%20cancer%20alone%20and%20every%20child%20has%20the%20chance%20to%20overcome%20life%E2%80%99s%20most%20difficult%20challenges%2C%20the%20lessons%20we%E2%80%99ve%20learnt%20over%20the%20years%20serve%20as%20a%20guidance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELooking%20to%20the%20future%3A%20Collaboration%20and%20compassion%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hans%20Foundation%20is%20strongly%20dedicated%20to%20increasing%20healthcare%20access%20for%20underprivileged%20children%2C%20but%20moving%20forward%20will%20require%20collaboration.%20By%20working%20together%2C%20healthcare%20providers%2C%20policymakers%2C%20and%20community%20organisations%20can%20enhance%20accessibility%2C%20affordability%2C%20and%20compassion%20in%20childhood%20cancer%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20renew%20our%20dedication%20to%20a%20future%20where%20healthcare%20inequities%20no%20longer%20hinder%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20chance%20at%20survival%20and%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20goal%20is%20evident%20and%20simple%20that%20every%20child%20should%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20have%20a%20complete%2C%20healthy%20life%20without%20being%20hindered%20by%20cancer.%20Drawing%20from%2015%20years%20of%20successful%20efforts%2C%20we%20progress%20with%20optimism%2C%20resolve%2C%20and%20an%20aspiration%20for%20a%20global%20environment%20where%20all%20children%20have%20equal%20opportunities%20to%20succeed%2C%20irrespective%20of%20their%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20contributed%20by%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%3B%20Written%20by%20Shweta%20Rawat%2C%20Founder%20%26amp%3B%20Chairperson%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThis%20content%20is%20submitted%20directly%20by%20the%20respective%20brand%2Forganisation.%20The%20Better%20India%E2%80%99s%20Editorial%20team%20is%20not%20involved%20in%20creating%20this%20article%20and%20is%20not%20responsible%20for%20its%20accuracy%20or%20consequences.%20For%20any%20concerns%2C%20please%20connect%20with%20the%20brand%20directly.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fmagazines%2Fpanache%2Finternational-child-cancer-day-more-than-400000-children-get-diagnosed-with-cancer-every-year%2